00:00:24.430 --> 00:00:27.530
Let me just draw the triangle
ahead of time.

00:00:27.530 --> 00:00:29.960
I'm going to use
fancy-- whoops.

00:00:29.960 --> 00:00:33.070
Actually, let me use
