00:00:33.070 --> 00:00:37.540
So this was the initial
vector.

00:00:37.540 --> 00:00:41.460
Then I wanted to do--
switch to green.

00:00:41.460 --> 00:00:42.670
This is its horizontal.

00:00:42.670 --> 00:00:44.070
I'm going to draw the
