So I'm going to draw my ground,
it's kind of a yellow

00:07:57.420 --> 00:07:58.820
ochre ground.

00:07:58.820 --> 00:08:09.790
And I'm going to shoot something
at an angle of 45

00:08:09.790 --> 00:08:15.960
degrees at 10 meters
per second.

00:08:15.960 --> 00:08:22.600
And we figured out that it
will go 20 meters and its

00:08:22.600 --> 00:08:25.630
